ime":"2019-08-21T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"幫辦係force好細粒既炸，改咩變，豬頭骨就有得你食"},{"pid":"cb8609011d28a2bb3297633cad63bc78f3b079e8","tid":1491647,"uid":71446,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"好似d中學訓練營咁，俾班阿sir糟質完3日兩夜，離開時成班同學喊住咁話唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警員訓練應該嚴重百倍"},{"pid":"3a3c9879d439942a51af768419191618045e8871","tid":1491647,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:31:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c7d4430c36ba3c9945b48da77032eae6e6525f1","tid":1491647,"uid":67332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:32:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以大家真係唔好打算單槍匹馬做學警，從內部改變警隊啦。一個人去好容易比人同化。你如果真係要咁做，有得考督察就考督察，仲要起碼四五個一齊去報，唔係全部收都唔入營，或者特登入營一兩個禮拜就quit。全部收的話，你入到班起碼有人同你照應，互相提醒；特登入營一兩個禮拜就quit的話，亦都可以打亂佢地嘅人力資源安排<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"8607a7e6524866bc115d15f6aa1f1e083d131a9e","tid":1491647,"uid":223639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb66401ebf0638d6427dc0732c886ba17fa1825","tid":1491647,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1552be60b770bf3953ef078ff1691b875ff74e9d","tid":1491647,"uid":114416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c7f4d37cf5dba806981a88897d4fc913d3c3eee","tid":1491647,"uid":118647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"773a710be8960104383f917beba2c2a31815b3e1","tid":1491647,"uid":114416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d6e9527f48ce561a39b04ef2b8e6ab938c46621","tid":1491647,"uid":5205,"like